%p Hello #{@course.user.username},

- if @course.approved?
  %p
    Great news! Your course
    %strong= link_to @course.title, @course
    has been
    %strong{ style: 'color: #28a745;' } approved
    and is now available for students to enroll.

  %p You can start promoting your course and track enrollments from your instructor dashboard.

- else
  %p
    Your course
    %strong= link_to @course.title, @course
    has been reviewed and is currently
    = succeed '.' do
      %strong{ style: 'color: #dc3545;' } not approved

  %p Please review your course content and ensure it meets our quality guidelines. You can resubmit for approval after making the necessary changes.

%p
  Best regards,
  %br
  The Corsego Team

%p{ style: 'font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d;' }= link_to 'Visit Corsego', root_url
